"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Withdrawal Limits\\n\\nIn an effort to reduce risk across the protocol, withdrawals can be rate limited and gated in specific circumstances.​\\n\\n## Withdrawal rate limits\\n\\nAs a default setting, withdrawals of Noble USDC are rate limited to max(1% of TVL, $1mm) per hour\\n\\nAs a default setting, withdrawals of Noble USDC are rate limited to max(10% of TVL, $10mm) per day\\n\\nThese rate limit parameters can be updated by governance.\\n\\n## Withdrawal gating\\n\\nAll subaccount transfers and withdrawals will be gated for 50 blocks if a negative collateralized subaccount is seen in state and/or can't be liquidated or deleveraged\\n\\nAll subaccount transfers and withdrawals will also be gated for 50 blocks if a 5+ minute chain outage occurs.\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/concepts/trading/limits/withdrawal-limits#withdrawal-limits\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>In an effort to reduce risk across the protocol, withdrawals can be rate limited and gated in specific circumstances.​</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/concepts/trading/limits/withdrawal-limits.mdx#withdrawal-limits\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nIn an effort to reduce risk across the protocol, withdrawals can be rate limited and gated in specific circumstances.​\\n\",\"title\":\"Withdrawal Limits\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/concepts/trading/limits/withdrawal-limits#withdrawal-rate-limits\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>As a default setting, withdrawals of Noble USDC are rate limited to max(1% of TVL, $1mm) per hour</p>\\n<p>As a default setting, withdrawals of Noble USDC are rate limited to max(10% of TVL, $10mm) per day</p>\\n<p>These rate limit parameters can be updated by governance.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/concepts/trading/limits/withdrawal-limits.mdx#withdrawal-rate-limits\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nAs a default setting, withdrawals of Noble USDC are rate limited to max(1% of TVL, $1mm) per hour\\nAs a default setting, withdrawals of Noble USDC are rate limited to max(10% of TVL, $10mm) per day\\nThese rate limit parameters can be updated by governance.\\n\",\"title\":\"Withdrawal rate limits\",\"titles\":[\"Withdrawal Limits\"]},{\"href\":\"/concepts/trading/limits/withdrawal-limits#withdrawal-gating\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>All subaccount transfers and withdrawals will be gated for 50 blocks if a negative collateralized subaccount is seen in state and/or can&#x27;t be liquidated or deleveraged</p>\\n<p>All subaccount transfers and withdrawals will also be gated for 50 blocks if a 5+ minute chain outage occurs.</p>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/concepts/trading/limits/withdrawal-limits.mdx#withdrawal-gating\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nAll subaccount transfers and withdrawals will be gated for 50 blocks if a negative collateralized subaccount is seen in state and/or can&#x27;t be liquidated or deleveraged\\nAll subaccount transfers and withdrawals will also be gated for 50 blocks if a 5+ minute chain outage occurs.\",\"title\":\"Withdrawal gating\",\"titles\":[\"Withdrawal Limits\"]}]}}"
